==纪念与遗迹==
戴喜云死后，英殖民地政府在槟城命名一条“戴喜云路（Jalan  Tye Kee Yoon）<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/liuruxia/25710956931 |title=槟城戴喜云路  |access-date=2016-09-13 |archive-date=2016-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104034512/https://www.flickr.com/photos/liuruxia/25710956931 |dead-url=no }}</ref>作为纪念。

大埔县城郊印山麓，建有戴公碑亭，纪念戴公<ref>廣東省志: 《华侨志》 - Page 345</ref>。

槟城时中分校旧址，当地人称为Goh Chan Lau（五层楼），原是一栋豪华的大厦，戴喜云在1908年买下，设立为大清国槟城领事馆<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pht.org.my/shih-chung-school-11-jalan-sultan-ahmad-shah/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-09-15 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029114328/https://pht.org.my/shih-chung-school-11-jalan-sultan-ahmad-shah/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

槟城的荷花河路（Leith Street）14号是[[张弼士|张弼士]]故居张弼士大厦，隔壁就是戴喜云故居戴喜云大厦[https://www.flickr.com/photos/23268776@N03/6302552374/in/photolist-aAWef7-4fmaan-e2Kyv2-EWJC3E-ErWt6p-FfUi6e-EWJJY3-Fn1mks-FmZXmG-ErzVDY-FfUfAV-FdBCZQ-FfU7FM-ErWkJR-FdBTZQ-ErzT35-FmZURw-FaZnJT-fbTqtm] {{Wayback|url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/23268776@N03/6302552374/in/photolist-aAWef7-4fmaan-e2Kyv2-EWJC3E-ErWt6p-FfUi6e-EWJJY3-Fn1mks-FmZXmG-ErzVDY-FfUfAV-FdBCZQ-FfU7FM-ErWkJR-FdBTZQ-ErzT35-FmZURw-FaZnJT-fbTqtm |date=20161013051820 }}<ref>[http://teochiewkia2010.blogspot.ca/2010/03/leith-street.html   槟城人]</ref>

